        "relations": null,
        "text": [
          " الْعِدَّةُ وَ الْحَيْضُ لِلنِّسَاءِ إِذَا ادَّعَتْ صُدِّقَتْ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Jameel, from Zurara, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The waiting period, and the menstruation are for the women; when they claim, they would be ratified’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Jamil from Zurarah who has said the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Waiting period and Hayd (menses) are for women. If they say something about it their words are accepted.”’ "
          ]
        }
      }
